text: Phos textus is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Buccinidae, the true whelks. ==Description== ==Distribution== This species is distributed in the Mascarene Basin. ==References== * Drivas, J. & M. Jay (1988). Coquillages de La Réunion et de l'île Maurice '' Category:Buccinidae Category:Gastropods described in 1791
title: Phos textus
